const Form = () => (





<form  className='form-container'onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
            <label>TITLE</label> 
            <input type='text' name='title' 
                placeholder='Insert a title...' value={input.title} onChange={handleChange}/>
            <label>DATE</label> 
            <input type='datetime-local' name='date' 
                placeholder='05/12/2035 12:17pm'value={input.date} onChange={handleChange}/>
            <label>VENUE</label> 
            <input type='text' name='venue' 
                placeholder='Insert a venue...' value={input.venue} onChange={handleChange}/> 
            <button type='submit' disabled={!input.title||!input.date||!input.venue}>Create</button>
        </form>

    
)

export default Form
